flowchart LR
    A["1. Browser bursts<br/>(unpredictable)"] --> B["2. Fire-and-forget API<br/>(204, no I/O)"]
    B --> C["3. Kafka buffer<br/>(absorbs spikes)"]
    C --> D["4. Dedup window<br/>(70-90% reduction)"]
    D --> E["5. OLAP storage<br/>(aggregate queries)"]
